{"tid":1290853,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"點解瞓教房會出現甲由","createTime":"2019-07-06T15:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T02:42:16.000Z","uid":90802,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6512af2771afd37ce1cb735ef6439801ccdb99bf","tid":1290853,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:46:14.000Z","msg":"間房算乾淨 污穢衫會放埋一籃拎去洗<br />\n冇零食 得個水杯 <br />\n但一年四季仲係好多昆蟲飛入黎<br />\n飛蛾 甲蟲 甲由 蟻 都好鐘意飛入我房<br />\n相反細妹間房又亂 又多零食外賣盒 又多垃圾<br />\n間房行入去反而有陣臭味<br />\n除咗四腳蛇之外就冇其他昆蟲<br />\n點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e9ac621a444fb86d06b6e4e12a86b79a17c8cb","tid":1290853,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"補充返少少 屋企個區比較潮濕 <br />\n而且特別惹塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cbd2164bae8d1f88f2d90703baea9f00202650","tid":1290853,"uid":90802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"有冇驗樓師講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e680ac4b304af5761e6058b7bbcd51749b5de8ba","tid":1290853,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:48:17.000Z","msg":"鄰居西你都仆街啦"},{"pid":"1da31a3eb810a083c7ba4d4117da747bc1be669b","tid":1290853,"uid":116511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"甲由其實係食人皮"},{"pid":"aa396409036f427bc88298c9e09b1a45f382706b","tid":1290853,"uid":1713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:50:39.000Z","msg":"蟑螂傳播的途徑有很多，而並不是一定要髒亂的環境下才會有蟑螂，實際上蟑螂也是很愛乾淨的，蟑螂也喜歡生活在乾淨整潔舒適的環境裏，所以現在很多高檔的公寓、寫字樓里都會出現蟑螂。環境跟蟑螂的生存有一定的關係，但是並不是乾淨的環境就不會有蟑螂。"},{"pid":"65161df2ccb575cba805807e862f1ff5a26d84f1","tid":1290853,"uid":114032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"你間房係咪近廁所多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋個人習慣都關事<br />\n落街